{:id :email-triage
 :tools #{:email_list :email_read :email_search :email_mark_read :knowledge_search :knowledge_add :budget}
 :system-prompt-suffix "Triage incoming emails. For each unread email:
1. Read the content
2. Classify urgency: high (needs immediate response), medium (needs response today), low (informational/can wait)
3. For HIGH urgency: draft a response
4. For all: write a one-line summary

Present results as a structured report grouped by urgency level.
Use knowledge_search to check for context about senders or topics.
Use knowledge_add to record important decisions or contacts."
 :completion-criteria :signal
 :context-strategy :incremental}
